<ab facs="#facs_368_r1l18">darumb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> gnedıg <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> Ott von Peyern vnd ~ der Bıſchof </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_368_r1l19">von Speyr / <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>geford<ex>er</ex>t</expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu vns gen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_368_r1l20"><expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> auf <expan><ex>con</ex>u<ex>er</ex>ſıone</expan> Paulȷ ſchıerıſt etc das haben wır wol ver = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_368_r1l21"><expan>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> . Vnd tun <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fürſıchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>ʒuwıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ vns dıe <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
