<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und gebetten habt von des tags
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, darumb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        gnedig <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Ott von Peyern und der bischof von Speyr
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>geford<ex>er</ex>t</expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> zu uns gen <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<app>
<note><q type="date">auf <expan><ex>con</ex>v<ex>er</ex>sione</expan> Paul
                                schierist</q>25.01.1421</note>
</app> etc., das haben wir wol <expan>vernome<ex>n</ex></expan> und tun
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fürsichtik<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>zu wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz uns die
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> auch <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und
                        den tag zu uns also <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kündt</expan> haben; und wissen
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> teils noch niht
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, denn daz <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
                        tag bey uns auf <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> zeit also fürsich geen
                        sülle. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
